* your theme is pointed and updated 

Open the Minima theme
	MacOS: open $(bundle info --path minima)
	Windows: explorer c:\Ruby26-x64\lib\rub\gems\2.6.3\gems\minima-2.5.1
	UPDATE: A viewer recommends this for Linux:
	"xdg" : Linux: xdc-open $(bundle info --path minima)
 go to theme folder then > layout > home.html
**** you can create a "home.html" file it will overwrite under "_sites" folder
you can drag and drop all files over to not use remote and it woud be local

